Now is the time….

Here’s a few of what we have sold in the last 6 months. 

If you have thought about buying or selling, hit the DM’s and let’s talk. 

Open conversations about the possibilities, but there truthfully is no better time than now. You can hear all the white noise you want about the market, but history shows now is the time. As soon as interest rates drop, chaos will ensue. 

Thoughts?

Chances are you have been waiting and looking for the right thing to post. 

The truth is…you already have the right thing to post right at your fingertips. It’s 99.9% likely it is already on your phone. Here’s the thing, quit worrying about what someone might think and just post it! 

I have just about every hesitation handler figured out in the real estate space, but when it came to my own social media I hesitated. Sometimes it may have been burn out, sometimes it may have been looking for the right content, sometimes it may have been the timing, but the truth is, just post it!

The algorithm will always be around, there is no one way to beat it, so just post it and smile, after all is captured your personal eye for a reason, made you smile for a reason, or resonated with you because of something, so it should work the same for those that see it after you post.

-Trent

If you are on the fence, now is the time. Slide into these DM’s with any of your real estate questions.

End of year high note ✅ 

This was the last closing of 2023 for me, I’ve found that the best way to start the following year fast is to keep the pedal down thru the month of December. 🙌🏼 So many times December 1st hits and agents check out for the year. 

This home set records and this proves that the market is busy whether it’s the week of Christmas or not. Good agents are productive year round. 📈

The market is trending upward, pressure is mounting with the FED outlining rates decreases in 2024. When that happens inventory is going to shrink and values are going to climb and climb fast.

If you have been on the fence about a buying or selling, slide into those DM’s and let us answer your questions.

Take a look at this 👀!

Offered at $575,000 💵 
3 Bedroom
2 Bathrooms
1,846 Sq. Ft. 📐 
2 Car Garage 🚘 

Location is in one of the most sought after subdivisions in the Prescott area. This home is semi updated allowing for a buyer to make the final updates of their choosing to make it their own! 

Tour it today before rates drop 📉 and values increase 📈! 

-Trent

Differentiate in 2024!

In growth comes change. The real estate market is one thing that is certain to always be changing. 

What worked in the past may not work in the future. You must differentiate in your path to success. No two agents are alike. You’ve most likely hired us because we differentiate from the normal agent. 

Understanding a clients need is crucial, but understanding the value you bring in unique thought, education for clients, negotiations for results, and taking the time to really delve into customer service for their needs are all factors to separate yourself from the pack. 

Be yourself and know your strengths.

-Trent
